{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "安魂教堂", "storyInfo": "樓上的塞茜莉亞哼唱古老的薩卡茲歌謠，歌聲散落風中。被稱為“先導”的修士向艾澤爾發問：為什麼只有薩科塔理當受福？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g4_laterano_cathedralliving", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臉色這麼差，通宵了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他回來了，我看到了，絕不會認錯......那種光，安多恩的源石技藝！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......所以這就是你昨天下午突然沒了消息的原因。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#9$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，他竟然直接找上你了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#9$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#9$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他不是來找我的。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天帶那個混血女孩回大教堂的路上......我遇到了薩卡茲。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種時候？薩卡茲？在拉特蘭大街上？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒錯。我去追薩卡茲，讓艾澤爾帶那個女孩回大教堂。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我追到法柏爾區邊緣......薩卡茲，被安多恩的源石技藝掩護，逃走了。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於艾澤爾，我以為他昨天就到大教堂了。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他沒來。這是他的終端。貼在一輛使節禮賓車的車底。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，那個見習小鬼演技有那麼好？把你騙過了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不認為那是演技。但我確實不明白他為什麼......難道，安多恩把他也擄走了......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲亞梅塔，我覺得你需要冷靜點。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很冷靜，我比這八年中的任何一分鐘都要冷靜！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們始終不肯告訴我，那天我離開之後的事情。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明只是個清剿任務......明明比預想中還要順利......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是接了一個臨時支援......離開了四個小時......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到那個廢墟的時候，什麼都遲了。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能和你講的都講過了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鎖與匙到底給了他什麼？能讓他瘋到對蕾繆安動手？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#11$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個，還真不是我不想告訴你......我也得知道啊。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#11$2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#11$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲亞梅塔，我們現在在拉特蘭，在拉特蘭大教堂，這裡不是什麼卡茲戴爾的野外廢墟。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該休息一下，菲亞梅塔。要不，我去幫你把年假請了？公證所的年假不用會過期的。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在開什麼玩笑？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#11$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後天就是會議開幕，安多恩帶著薩卡茲出現在拉特蘭城，擄走了一個混血薩科塔女孩，甚至可能對執行者動了手......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我大意了，看那個薩卡茲對法柏爾區的熟悉程度，他們在拉特蘭應該已經潛伏很久了......這個瘋子到底又打算幹什麼！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說真的，冷靜點，菲亞梅塔。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$2"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#9$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老傢伙已經知道迷途者的消息了，薇爾麗芙也知道。我昨天在大教堂也是工作了的——雖然我不是很喜歡把開會叫做工作。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#9$2"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總而言之，拉特蘭沒你想得那麼危險。安多恩也只是個薩科塔而已，沒有六隻眼睛四條胳膊。你要真想對付他，現在去休息兩個小時。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我們去找蕾繆安。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_213_mostma_1#2$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你還沒有完全失去理智。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#2$2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g6_laterano_chapelin", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨晚休息得怎麼樣？", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我休息得很好。謝謝你收留我們，先生。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安魂教堂的門永遠敞開，只要你不嫌棄這裡太過壓抑。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，生者和死者都會到訪這裡。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......此時能有一處容身之所已經很難得了。說起來，塞茜莉亞......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你帶來的女孩，對嗎？姐妹們告訴我，她昨晚睡得很沉，大概是累了吧。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許她度過了太漫長的一天。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾哥哥，修士先生，早上好。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上好，塞茜莉亞，你好像精神不錯。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯......畢竟，今天還有事情要做。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我向修士先生拜託了一件事。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修士先生告訴我，來到這裡的......去世的人，會有和親人告別的儀式。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想和媽媽......好好道個別......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#4$