", "attributes": {"content": "會晃得晚上睡不著！雖然看故事書很方便......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你和爸爸是一個地方來的嗎？為什麼我爸爸不能住在城裡？為什麼拉特蘭沒有其他薩卡茲？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我的名字叫塞茜莉亞！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你好，塞茜莉亞。就叫我......羅塞菈吧。", "name": "薩卡茲女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......修士，薩卡茲為什麼會出現在這裡？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是啊，薩卡茲......神聖的拉特蘭城，從不允許薩卡茲踏足。）", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那麼，塞茜莉亞又是什麼人呢？）", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（走吧，給她們一點空間。）", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......你們想做什麼？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我們......只是在尋找自己的路。）", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_092"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先導，早上好。", "name": "虔誠的信徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_092"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先導，向您致敬。", "name": "思索的信徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_065#1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先導，祝您健康。", "name": "微笑的信徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_065#1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們叫你先導。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不如此自居，你可以稱呼我的名字，安多恩。", "name": "修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我的兄弟姐妹們而言，如果擁有一個先導能讓他們感到安心，獲得方向，我願意盡一份責任，僅此而已。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願如此。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你在想什麼。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個潛伏在拉特蘭的異教組織和他們蠱惑人心的領導者，打算在拉特蘭精心籌備的會議期間策劃一場驚天陰謀，是嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們只是敞開大門而已。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被厭棄的，被損毀的，被侮辱的，被褻瀆的......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安魂教堂接納所有人。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，你，我，我們是“天使”，他們不是，屬於薩科塔的神殿和聖堂中沒有他們的位置。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#4$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看他，那個釘棺材的烏薩斯老人，在戰爭中失去了親人、朋友、土地、故鄉。他能依靠什麼，相信什麼？他能從哪裡獲得安慰和救贖？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跨越漫長的旅途，他來到拉特蘭，來到他偶然從旅行者口中得知的遍灑聖樂和光輝的安樂之鄉。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這裡能給他什麼？輝煌的拉特蘭城如何安慰這被厄運壓得佝僂的異國人？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到那個正在給草藥澆水的卡普里尼女人了嗎，因為得罪貴族，背上了蕩婦和褻瀆者的駡名，掙扎著從被點燃的房子中逃了出來。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只是想要獲得平靜，或許再奢侈一點，偶爾享受片刻的悠閒和歡愉。——大教堂中的堂皇聖徒們會承認她為姐妹嗎？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對這些人，我們榮耀的拉特蘭市民們或許會報以同情的微笑，也許熱忱地傾聽，甚至慷慨地敞開錢包，展現自己仁慈的美德。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但所有這一切——隔岸觀火，他們永遠只會隔岸觀火。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於薩卡茲，“被詛咒的魔族佬”，“奸詐殘忍的魔族佬”......從未有過選擇的“魔族佬”。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們與我們的仇恨持續了千百年，自有史可考之日，薩科塔與薩卡茲就相互屠戮。最初的緣由埋沒在塵埃，彼此的仇視已成為常理。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父子處決另一對父子，姐妹殺死另一雙姐妹，薩卡茲以襲擊薩科塔的商隊為樂，薩科塔以洞穿薩卡茲的胸膛為榮。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們盡情塑造著自己眼中的他們，卻對他們眼中的自己毫無興趣，復仇，反擊，行為積累為習俗，習俗堆積成傳統......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，若你願意與他們共處一片穹頂之下，你會發現他們的悲喜與我們並無不同。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為歸來歡樂，因離去哭泣，會揶揄朋友，也會羞澀於愛情，有人愛喝酒、愛唱歌，也有人願意與信仰同行......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到底有多大的歧異與不同？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在拉特蘭，即使是那些虔誠篤信的黎博利修士，小心翼翼地遵守每一條戒律，執行每一次儀式，獲封為聖賢，晉升為樞機......", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教廷也從未真正接納他們，黎博利們不過是解決俗事的幫手，處理庶務的工具。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們沒有這一頂光環，他們就不是......呵，“被選中”的薩科塔。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平和美麗、充滿歡笑的拉特蘭，這份“恩典”，只有我們配得享有。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你說的......未免......離經叛道......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的執行者，我問你，為什麼——", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有薩科塔理當受福？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們知道塞茜莉亞的身份。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多年之前，我就知道了。一個薩科塔和薩卡茲的混血兒，若世上真有恩典，她才是。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那你們現在想擄走塞茜莉亞，是因為使節們的會議？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個會議與我們無關。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在才來迎接塞茜莉亞，只為了孩子能在母親身邊成長。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做完該做的事，我們就會離開拉特蘭。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你要做什麼。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你似乎很警惕......首先要完成的，是塞茜莉亞母親的葬禮。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到了嗎，前面那片開滿野花的地方？那是墓地。明天，費莉亞就會安葬在那裡。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若人人死而平等——", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理當生也如此。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g10_laterano_roof", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出來。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者費德里科。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬國信使閣下，你是否為薩卡茲提供了潛入拉特蘭周邊的管道？若屬實，我將把你移送至教皇廳有關機構接受問訊。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們不必鬧得那麼僵。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請配合公證所工作，若拒捕，我將依據有關條例暫時褫奪貴方拉特蘭公民權益。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基於律法和聖訓，我們該如何解釋這次相會？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應當解釋為一次考驗，還是一次迷途呢？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抑或，迷途也不過是考驗的一部分？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_373_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_279_excu_4"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是明確的拒捕行為。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，看來我們不能和平解決了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "char_279_excu_4"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}